data.description: Completely updated 3 Bedroom 2 1/2 Bath 2 Story home located in the highly desirable Meadows at Canal Winchester.  Open Floor Plan features a gorgeous updated Kitchen with all new granite countertops and tile backsplash, abundant cabinet and counter space, central island and stainless steel appliances!  Spacious Family Room with vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace!  Upstairs you will find a large Owner's Suite with Walk in Closet and EnSuite Bath with new vanity, shower and flooring along with 2 additional Bedrooms and updated Full Bath!  Finished partial Basement allows for additional living space!  Private back yard with mature trees!  New flooring throughout, new lighting fixtures and new exterior painting!  Schedule your showings ASAP as this home won't last!
